591
00:37:58,390 --> 00:37:59,850
Thank you, Your Highness.

592
00:38:04,570 --> 00:38:05,540
Your Majesty!

593
00:38:06,940 --> 00:38:08,300
Yi Qingyun.

594
00:38:08,340 --> 00:38:10,200
So, you were planning an ambush!

595
00:38:11,740 --> 00:38:13,220
I see you don't want to...

