614
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:49,260
Let me see if there's anything for your eyes.

615
00:39:53,140 --> 00:39:55,060
Quite the medicine pouch he has.

616
00:39:59,340 --> 00:40:00,580
That's quite a lot of medicine.

617
00:40:00,580 --> 00:40:02,110
Want to play a guessing game

618
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:03,620
